# tools/ holds project-local toolchain binaries that we vendor rather
# than rely on the developer's PATH for. Per PROP-000 §16, JTD codegen
# lives here. The binaries themselves are NOT committed — each
# subdirectory carries a README.md pinning the upstream version and
# install procedure. New machines run the install command from the
# README to populate this directory.
*
!.gitignore
!*/
!*/README.md
